Package: @ft-transcendence/observability
Version: 1.0.0
Build Date: 2025-06-30 01:02:29 UTC
Build Host: cachyos-x8664
Node Version: v22.16.0
NPM Version: 11.4.2

Features:
- Prometheus metrics collection
- Structured JSON logging with Pino
- Built-in health checks (/health)
- Request tracing and correlation
- Enhanced error handling
- TypeScript support
- Docker integration
- Microservices ready

Installation:
1. Extract archive: tar -xzf ft-transcendence-observability-1.0.0.tar.gz
2. Install in your service: npm install file:./ft-transcendence-observability-1.0.0
3. Import in your code: import { setupObservability } from '@ft-transcendence/observability';
4. Setup: setupObservability(app, 'your-service-name');

For detailed instructions, see INSTALL.md
